		<description>A dryad caste specialized in shedding a lightweight leathery material. Used as part of their mating ritual, this leather can also be harvested and used by humans.\n\nIn general, dryads are mammal-like creatures that have a symbiotic relationship with the Gauranlen tree. They reproduce together with their tree, which contains a hidden dryad queen. Dryads can morph into various specialized castes.</description>
